<a href="http://32bit.me/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/pic1.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1497" title="pic1" src="http://32bit.me/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/pic1-300x187.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="187" /></a>

